snippet.title: Winning Eleven 2002 - Intro (Queen-We Will Rock You)
snippet.description:
This is the intro of World Soccer Winning Eleven 2002 (WE2002), for PSX (only in Japan :(  )

Maybe the best intro ever of WE/PES series...

Watch in HQ:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wtktxKLvo68&fmt=18

Direct rip from the game
